The '''Colossal Hydra''' is a [[superior]] variant of the [[hydra]]. It has a chance of spawning after purchasing the unlock ''Bigger and Badder'' for 150 [[Slayer reward point]]s from any [[Slayer master]].

In combat, the Colossal Hydra will occasionally shoot out an electric lightning attack. The lightning will come as two pools chasing the player for some time, dealing modest damage and [[Stun (status)|paralysing]] the player if struck. The spell [[Vengeance]] does not work against the Colossal Hydra special attack.

==Drops==
''In addition to 100% drops and tertiary drops, superior slayer monsters will always roll 3 additional items, of which only 1 roll may be from the superior unique table. The other rolls are performed on the regular counterpart's table; their displayed drop chances represent a single roll.''

